#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:5 0409e7e78fbe4633baa89aff8b1ee9dd
msgid "User Buffer Registration"
msgstr "用户缓冲区注册"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:7 71e7d40378b7407dabf6ee46f0b50eeb
msgid ""
"User Buffer Registration is a feature that allows NCCL to directly send/receive/operate data through the user buffer "
"without extra internal copy. It can accelerate collectives and reduce the resource usage (e.g. #channel usage)."
msgstr "用户缓冲区注册是一项功能，允许 NCCL 直接通过用户缓冲区发送/接收/操作数据，无需额外的内部复制。它可以加速集合操作并减少资源使用（例如，#通道使用）。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:10 af4307277ed24ee283b9182a479a9931
msgid ""
"NCCL 2.19.x now supports user buffer registration for NVLink Switch; any NCCL collectives that support NVLS algorithm "
"can utilize this feature. To enable the *CUDA Graph based* buffer registration, users have to comply with several "
"requirements:"
msgstr "NCCL 2.19.x现在支持NVLink Switch的用户缓冲区注册；任何支持NVLS算法的NCCL集合都可以利用这一功能。要启用基于CUDA图形的缓冲区注册，用户必须符合几项要求："

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:13 ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:21
#: 4bf9cd60c3b8410fa3ff04068935f9fb 9f26cb50da63447ba0ad67215e36a672
msgid "The buffer is allocated through :c:func:`ncclMemAlloc()`."
msgstr "缓冲区是通过 :c:func:`ncclMemAlloc()` 分配的。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:14 adecc4df6f394bc08f6a58d30c49a2fc
msgid "Offset to the head address of the buffer is same for each rank in collectives."
msgstr "缓冲区的头地址偏移对于集体操作中的每个排名都是相同的。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:15 50d25da16a5d4b1cbdb01583864b4b06
msgid "The NCCL operation is launched on a stream captured by a CUDA graph."
msgstr "NCCL 操作在被 CUDA 图捕获的流上启动。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:17 7a6c2237c5fa404da20cb1ae1a022187
msgid "Registered buffers will be deregistered when cuda graph is destroyed."
msgstr "当CUDA图被销毁时，已注册的缓冲区将被取消注册。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:19 f02b91d7321e409aa1033e35d8da25f4
msgid ""
"On the other hand, to enable the *Local based* buffer registration, users have to comply with the following "
"requirements:"
msgstr "另一方面，要启用*基于本地的*缓冲区注册，用户必须遵守以下要求："

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:22 269811580fa04c57baef0af96e23173b
msgid "Register buffer with :c:func:`ncclCommRegister` before calling collectives."
msgstr "在调用集合操作之前，使用:c:func:`ncclCommRegister`注册缓冲区。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:23 7d6b1ac1dc564fd496594a6b9b6b4f2f
msgid "Call NCCL collectives as usual but similarly keep the offset to the head address of the buffer same for each rank."
msgstr "按照惯例调用 NCCL 集合，但是同样保持每个排名的偏移量与缓冲区的头地址相同。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:25 314c2a5caabf4336b6cb794b1505654e
msgid "Registered buffers will be deregistered when users explicitly call :c:func:`ncclCommDeregister`."
msgstr "当用户显式调用 :c:func:`ncclCommDeregister` 时，已注册的缓冲区将被注销。"
